data.description: Located in the heart of Bensalem awaits your next home and just in the time for the holidays! 5656 Cricket Lane boasts just above 2,000 square feet of comfort and space. Step into a warm and inviting foyer that is adjoined by a formal dining room to the left and a large living space to the right. This space has incredible natural lighting, a perfect view of your front yard and is a perfect blank canvas awaiting your personal design. Continuing through your tour, you'll find a contemporary kitchen with a peninsula layout, stainless steel appliances, wood cabinets and granite countertops.  An open concept family room seamlessly connects to your kitchen, making this 1st floor perfect for entertaining. Step through your sliding doors to find plenty of space to withdraw into the privacy of your own gated backyard. Upstairs you'll find 4 spacious bedrooms with ample closet space in each bedroom and 2 full bathrooms, one of which is an ensuite to the primary bedroom. The home comes complete with a powder room on the first floor, laundry room, finished basement and additional workspace, which can be converted to suit your needs. The home's location is convenient to all that Bensalem has to offer. Whether you're wanting a night at Parx Casino, a dinner for two at a local eatery or a quick trip to the Neshaminy Mall, all of your major needs are less than a 10-minute commute away! With mortgage rates continuing to rise and inventory still historically low, you don't want to miss out on the opportunity to lock in on this wonderful opportunity to call this incredible property, home sweet home. Schedule your tours today!
